[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0106","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2861","title":"Adobe ColdFusion 管理员控制台目录遍历漏洞","description":"Adobe ColdFusion 9.0.1 及更早版本的管理员控制台（位于 /CFIDE/administrator/ 下多个页面）在处理 locale 参数时存在多个目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可在未认证的情况下，通过向 mappings.cfm、logging/settings.cfm、datasources/index.cfm、j2eepackaging/editarchive.cfm 及 enter.cfm 等页面的 locale 参数注入包含 ../ 的恶意路径，绕过目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件，进而可能获取配置文件、密码等敏感信息，造成信息泄露。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2861"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-08-11","updated":"2010-08-11","remediation":"升级到 Adobe 已修复的 ColdFusion 版本：ColdFusion 9.0.1 应用 APSB10-18 安全更新，ColdFusion 9.0/8.x 升级至对应补丁版本；同时限制对 /CFIDE/administrator/ 目录的访问，并对 locale 参数做路径规范化校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T19:33:34.451687758+00:00","references":["https://www.adobe.com/support/security/bulletins/apsb10-18.html","https://www.gnucitizen.org/blog/coldfusion-directory-traversal-faq-cve-2010-2861/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2010-2861"],"poc_urls":["https://www.gnucitizen.org/blog/coldfusion-directory-traversal-faq-cve-2010-2861/"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0102","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2920","title":"Joomla! Foobla Suggestions 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 组件 Foobla Suggestions 1.5.1.2 存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22），攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入目录遍历序列（如 ../）读取服务器任意文件。该漏洞影响使用该组件的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 6.8（中危），攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意 controller 参数实现任意文件读取，可能导致敏感配置文件、源代码泄露。ExploitDB 已收录公开利用代码。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2920"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-30T20:30:03.927","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:45.433","remediation":"升级或卸载存在漏洞的 Foobla Suggestions (com_foobla_suggestions) 组件 1.5.1.2 版本，或替换为其修复版本（需过滤 controller 参数中的 \"../\" 等目录穿越字符）。若无法立即更新，可在 Joomla! 后台禁用该组件，并通过 .htaccess 添加规则拒绝 index.php 请求中携带 \"controller=../\" 或 NULL 字节等穿越序列，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlafoobla-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12120","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39341","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1844","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57660","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12120","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2920.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2920.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2920.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2920.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-2920-1980.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-2920.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2920_10.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d6a37376bba332b033eeef800cc2b5fc0701d843/CVE/data/2010/CVE-2010-2920.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/13/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/tholian-network/vulnerabilities/blob/cd8798a37e6d58633681c9596bee14e4189ad0e9/database/vulnerability/CVE-2010-2920.json","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2920.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0101","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2918","title":"Joomla! Visites 组件 远程文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Visites 组件 1.1 RC2 版本的 core/include/myMailer.class.php 文件存在 PHP 远程文件包含漏洞，攻击者可通过 mosConfig_absolute_path 参数传入恶意 URL，引入并执行任意 PHP 代码。该漏洞影响 Joomla! Visites 1.1 RC2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），属于 CWE-94 代码注入类别。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意 URL 参数实现远程代码执行，攻击者可完全控制受影响服务器。ExploitDB 已公开该漏洞的利用代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2918"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-30T20:30:03.847","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:45.213","remediation":"立即卸载或升级存在漏洞的 Joomla! Visites (com_joomla-visites) 组件 1.1 RC2 至官方修复版本（或移除该组件）；若暂无法升级，可在 php.ini 中设置 allow_url_fopen=Off 与 allow_url_include=Off 禁用远程文件包含，并在 Web 服务器层面使用 .htaccess 限制对 components/com_joomla-visites/ 目录的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/0804-exploits/joomlavisites-rfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14476","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/28942","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1925","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/42025","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14476","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2918.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2918.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2918.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2918.js","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-2918-1976.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-2918-1977.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bc11f954f9294701a2f089a93a32a20256e69591/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2918.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Dec/11/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Joomla/CVE-2010-2918.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-2918_1.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/cve-2010-2918.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0101.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0101.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0100","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2857","title":"Joomla! Music Manager 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Music Manager 组件存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞（CWE-22）。该组件在处理 album.html 页面时未对 cid 参数进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可通过在 cid 参数中注入 \"../\"（点点点）目录遍历序列，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、密码哈希等敏感数据），并可能借此造成其他未明确的危害。该漏洞影响使用存在缺陷的 Music Manager 组件的所有 Joomla! 站点，攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下即可通过构造特制请求远程发起攻击，CVSS 评分为 6.8，危害等级为中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2857"],"sources":["nuclei","exploit-db","cve"],"published":"2010-07-24","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用存在漏洞的 Joomla! Music Manager 第三方组件；若必须继续使用，请在组件 album.html 中对 cid 参数使用 intval() 强制取整并过滤 \"../\" 等路径穿越字符，同时升级到官方已修复该缺陷的版本。临时缓解措施包括在 Joomla 全局配置中将 PHP 的 allow_url_include 设为 Off，并将组件目录文件权限设为只读。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1007-exploits/joomlamusicmanager-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14274","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41485","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/60195","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2857.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0099","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2682","title":"Joomla Realtyna Translator 组件 目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Realtyna Translator（com_realtyna）组件 1.0.15 存在目录遍历（任意文件读取/本地文件包含）漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤校验，攻击者可构造包含「../」（点-点-斜杠）序列的恶意参数，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源码等敏感信息），甚至可能进一步造成本地文件包含等其他影响。该漏洞影响使用 com_realtyna 1.0.15 组件的 Joomla! 站点，远程未经身份认证的攻击者仅需发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用，无需任何权限或用户交互，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2682"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-12T13:27:28.097","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:18.330","remediation":"立即升级 Realtyna Translator (com_realtyna) 组件至官方修复版本，或卸载/禁用该组件（Extensions → Manage → Disable）；无法立即升级时，在 Web 应用防火墙或 .htaccess 中拦截 index.php?option=com_realtyna 请求中包含「../」的 controller 参数，并限制 PHP 对网站目录及系统文件的读取权限以缓解任意文件读取风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlarealtyna-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14017","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39337","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57647","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14017","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2682.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0098","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2680","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16353,\"outputTokens\":36,\"totalTokens\":16389}}","description":"Joomla! 的 JExtensions JE Section/Property Finder（jesectionfinder）组件存在目录遍历漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 view 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可在 view 参数中插入 \"../\" 等目录遍历序列，从而包含并执行目标服务器上的任意本地文件。攻击无需身份认证，仅需向受影响站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可导致敏感信息泄露甚至远程代码执行。受影响范围为安装了该缺陷组件的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2680"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-12T13:27:27.923","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:15.113","remediation":"建议立即在 Joomla! 后台 Extensions→Manage 中卸载或禁用存在漏洞的 jesectionfinder 组件，该第三方商业扩展官方已不再维护且无安全更新；若必须保留使用，应修补 components/com_jesectionfinder/ 下对 view 参数的处理代码，改用 JInput 获取输入并配合 basename() 或白名单机制仅允许加载预设视图文件，严禁解析含 \"../\" 的目录遍历序列；作为临时缓解，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache 的 .htaccess 或 Nginx 的 rewrite 规则）中拦截对 /component/jesectionfinder/ 路径中含 \"../\" 或 null 字节的请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1006-exploits/joomlajesectionfinder-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14064","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41163","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/59796","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14064","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2680.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2680.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2680.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2680.js","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/b6470123a7d8a7a3e512a294dd5d252afb3fc5a2/CVE-2010/CVE-2010-26xx/CVE-2010-2680.json","https://github.com/0xAwali/Virtual-Host/blob/a2988987751a6ab1f30d71e0d002b7af148c5c79/Templates/CVE/CVE-2010-2680.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-2680-1955.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-2680.rules","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-2680-1959.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/889686929cb8269a754b7b9536317f741fc92ddc/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2680.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2680_28.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0098.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0098.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0097","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0097.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2507","title":"Joomla! Picasa2Gallery 组件本地文件包含漏洞（LFI）","description":"Picasa2Gallery（com_picasa2gallery）组件 1.2.8 及更早版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传入包含 ../ 的路径序列，绕过目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如 /etc/passwd），并可能包含并执行本地文件造成进一步影响。攻击仅需构造特制 HTTP 请求，无需认证，利用条件为开启该组件且 PHP 未有效禁用空字节截断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2507"],"sources":["nuclei","cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2010-06-28","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"升级 Picasa2Gallery 组件到官方修复版本，或在 index.php 入口过滤 controller 参数中的 ../ 及空字节（%00），并配置 Joomla! 全局输入过滤以阻止目录遍历。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T18:42:14.489321313+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2010-2507","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/13981","http://secunia.com/advisories/40297","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41031","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/59669","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1006-exploits/joomlapicasa2gallery-lfi.txt"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/13981","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1006-exploits/joomlapicasa2gallery-lfi.txt"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/13981"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0097.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0096","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2307","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16403,\"outputTokens\":45,\"totalTokens\":16448}}","description":"Motorola SURFBoard SBV6120E 电缆调制解调器固件 SBV6X2X-1.0.0.5-SCM-02-SHPC 的 Web 服务器存在多个目录遍历漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可通过在 URL 请求中使用多重前导斜杠（//）、点点序列（../）或编码后的点点序列，绕过路径限制读取设备文件系统上的任意文件。该漏洞源于 Web 服务器对用户输入的路径参数缺乏有效规范化与过滤，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，可导致敏感配置文件、日志文件或系统文件泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0（中危），影响固件版本 SBV6X2X-1.0.0.5-SCM-02-SHPC 的 Motorola SURFBoard SBV6120E 设备。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2307"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-06-16T20:30:02.717","updated":"2026-06-16T23:20:30.680","remediation":"建议联系运营商（ISP）推送或升级 Motorola SURFBoard SBV6120E 至修复该目录遍历漏洞的新版固件（高于受影响的 SBV6X2X-1.0.0.5-SCM-02-SHPC 版本）；过渡期间在边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL，禁止从 WAN 侧及公网访问设备管理地址（默认 192.168.100.1 的 80 端口），仅放行受信任的内网主机，并关闭设备不必要的远程 Web 管理功能以阻断 `///`、`../` 及编码形式的任意文件读取。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/40054","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12865","http://www.osvdb.org/65249","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40550","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/59113","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12865","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2307.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2307.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2307.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2307.js","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-2307-1943.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd295775