verity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2128"],"sources":["nuclei","cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2010-06-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该组件官方未发布修复版本，建议立即在 Joomla 后台禁用并卸载 JE Quotation Form（com_jequoteform）组件；若必须保留，应对 index.php 中 view 参数实施严格的路径白名单校验，过滤并拒绝包含「../」、空字节及绝对路径等目录遍历字符的输入，并升级 Joomla 核心至受支持的最新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T17:14:00.476421223+00:00","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39832","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12607","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40187","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58593"],"poc_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12607"],"exp_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12607"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0094.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0093","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0093.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2122","title":"Joomla! Component simpledownload 0.9.5本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! com_simpledownload组件0.9.5版本存在目录穿越漏洞，攻击者可通过将controller参数设置为../遍历路径，读取任意本地文件如/etc/passwd。该漏洞源于未充分验证的用户输入允许访问不受限制的文件系统路径。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2122"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2010-06-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级Joomla! Component simpledownload至0.9.6或更高版本，启用path traversal防护，使用白名单文件访问机制验证用户输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T17:09:48.192371457+00:00","references":["http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/directory-a-documentation/downloads/10717","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlasimpledownload-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39871"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0093.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0092","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0092.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2050","title":"Joomla! Moron Solutions MS Comment 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Moron Solutions MS Comment（com_mscomment）组件 0.8.0b 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，即可通过向 index.php 传递包含“..”（点点）序列的 controller 参数，绕过路径限制读取目标服务器上的任意文件，如配置文件、源码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响所有运行该组件 0.8.0b 版本的 Joomla! 站点，攻击仅需构造恶意 HTTP 请求即可完成，利用门槛低、危害较大，CVSS 评分为 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2050"],"sources":["cve","nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-25T18:30:01.987","updated":"2010-05-25T18:30:01.987","remediation":"升级 Moron Solutions MS Comment 组件到支持官方补丁的版本，如升级至 0.8.0c 或更高版本。如无法立即升级，可配置 Web 服务器禁止目录遍历操作，过滤包含 '../' 或 '..' 的请求参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlamscomment-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12611","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40185","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1159","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58619","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2050.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0092.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2010/EXP-AVE-2010-0092.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0092.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0091","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0091.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2045","title":"Joomla! FDione Form Wizard 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! FDione Form Wizard 1.0.2 组件在处理 controller 参数时存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过 index.php?option=com_dioneformwizard&controller=../../etc/passwd 等路径构造读取服务器任意文件，泄露敏感信息如系统配置文件、用户凭证等。攻击无需认证即可远程利用，影响 Joomla! 使用该组件的所有网站。漏洞源于组件未对用户输入的 controller 参数进行充分验证和规范化处理，导致路径穿越安全隐患。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2045"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2010-05-25T18:30:01.797","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:52.663","remediation":"立即升级 Joomla! FDione Form Wizard 到安全补丁版本 1.6 或更高版本，通过官方网站 dionesoft.com/products/dione_form_wizard/product.html 获取最新安全更新。如无法立即更新，建议禁用该组件或通过 Web 应用防火墙禁止对 index.php 文件的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/64633","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlafdione-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39755","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12595","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40166","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58574","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2045.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2045.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2045.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2045.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-2045-1921.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5df5af06e079a6824349b336150de94d9ba1e7f8/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2045.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2045_27.yaml","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2010-2045"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0091.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0090","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2037","title":"Joomla! Percha Downloads Attach 组件 目录遍历 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Joomla! 组件 Percha 下载附件 1.1 存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过操控控制器参数实现任意文件读取。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 所有版本，攻击者只需向系统发送包含 \"..\" 的参数即可利用，从而严重威胁网站文件安全，可能导致机密信息泄露和系统进一步破坏。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2037"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-25T14:30:01.687","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:51.737","remediation":"tags<value>建议立即升级或卸载存在漏洞的 Percha Downloads Attach (com_perchadownloadsattach) 组件 1.1 版本，更换为官方已修复的版本；若暂无法升级，可在 Joomla 后台禁用或卸载该组件，并在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中禁止对 index.php 的 controller 参数传入包含 \"../\" 的路径，同时设置 open_basedir 限制 PHP 文件访问范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlaperchada-lfi.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40244","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34005","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2037.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2037.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2037.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5df5af06e079a6824349b336150de94d9ba1e7f8/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2037.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-2037-1916.yaml","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/f29605a96fd1261602d83e1b34d001cc853a7340/nvdcve/CVE-2010-2037.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2037_5.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Oct/23/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-2037_3.yaml","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--903ada19-28ee-4abc-b832-ac86584dbf6a.json","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2037.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0090.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0089","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0089.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2036","title":"Joomla! Percha Fields Attach 组件目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Joomla! Percha Fields Attach（com_perchafieldsattach）组件 1.x 版本存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。该组件在处理 index.php 传入的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，攻击者可在参数中插入 \"../\" 序列，突破 Web 根目录限制实现路径穿越。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、敏感数据等），并可能造成其他未明确的影响。该漏洞影响所有使用存在缺陷版本的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 基础评分 7.5，危害等级为高，攻击条件仅需能访问目标 Web 应用且无需任何权限，利用方式简单、危害显著。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2036"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-25T14:30:01.657","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:51.623","remediation":"卸载废弃的Percha Fields Attach组件，升级到Joomla!5.0+最新版本，确保系统组件仅保留官方维护的扩展包，并通过.htaccess和权限控制禁用文件访问路径，防止其他相同目录遍历漏洞的再次利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlaperchafa-lfi.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40244","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34004","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2036.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2036.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2036.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5df5af06e079a6824349b336150de94d9ba1e7f8/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2036.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-2036-1913.yaml","https://github.com/b1ank1108/VulSentinel/blob/12fae384c4fef6ba595f65eae09dc323d97a95f4/reports/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2036.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2036_29.yaml","https://github.com/Ciyfly/woodpecker/blob/f88bed6da55238547a423ce17dccb2cdbc93be50/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-